{"tid":2100793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"趙立堅：美國是最大麻煩製造者　蓬佩奧有何顏面談信譽？","createTime":"2020-07-09T10:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T11:11:07.000Z","uid":7542,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d52a0349977a7b19273ab00a5395d23362e8dbeb","tid":2100793,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:02:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>我覺得講得太好了 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧日前批評北京承諾給予香港50年高度自治，變成空頭支票；又指責中方沒有向全世界交代新型冠狀病毒的真相、並指中印早前的衝突，是一場難以置信的侵略行動。在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅指，<strong>美國近年打著「美國優先」的旗號，背棄自身的國際承諾和國際義務，已經成為最大的「麻煩製造者」，批評美方自身誠信掃地之下，蓬佩奧還有甚麼顏面和勇氣談論信譽</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅又指，美國累積確診病例已經超過300萬宗，美國政府對此有不可推卸的責任，強調中方在疫情發生後，第一時間向世衛組織通報，<strong>批評蓬佩奧視而不見、捏造事實掩蓋不了美方自身抗疫不力的失誤。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536811-20200709.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536811-20200709.htm&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=37ea2279\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536811-20200709.htm&h=7f36d9f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536811-20200709.htm</a>"},{"pid":"05de3bd367c297fab86691c633d97fd656aaa5b2","tid":2100793,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:03:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\">咩叫操控選舉？唔該每個人睇一睇：</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0ggBftnYDQ4&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmsv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=73210e47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4</a>"},{"pid":"27bb8248233316a6a9e63e70992edfda779c00a8","tid":2100793,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sco